          <div class="ex-title__textTwo">Выставка</div>
        </div>
        <div class="exhibition__content">
          <div class="ex-content__left">
            <img src="../src/assets/image/ex-cask.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="ex-content__right">
            <div class="ex__text">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Faucibus tortor tristique
